   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "# T05 DiD -- 最低工资政策对青年就业的影响\n",
    "\n",
    "## 0. 论文信息\n",
    "\n",
    "| 字段 | 内容 |\n",
    "|------|------|\n",
    "| **论文题目** | Minimum Wages and Employment in China |\n",
    "| **作者** | Ting Fang & Carl Lin |\n",
    "| **期刊** | *IZA Journal of Labor Policy*, 4(1), 1-30, 2015 |\n",
    "| **核心问题** | 提高最低工资是否降低青年就业率？ |\n",
    "| **方法** | 双重差分(DiD)，利用各城市最低工资调整的时间差异 |"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "f7ffc15d",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 1. 研究设计\n",
    "\n",
    "$$\\text{ATT} = (\\bar{Y}_{\\text{treat,post}} - \\bar{Y}_{\\text{treat,pre}}) - (\\bar{Y}_{\\text{ctrl,post}} - \\bar{Y}_{\\text{ctrl,pre}})$$\n",
    "\n",
    "**关键假设**：平行趋势——若无政策，处置组与对照组就业趋势应平行。\n",
    "\n",
    "**回归形式**：$Y_{it} = \\alpha_i + \\lambda_t + \\delta \\cdot \\text{treat}_i \\times \\text{post}_t + \\varepsilon_{it}$"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "id": "b5532f89",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "## 2. 数学理论\n",
    "\n",
    "**一致性条件**：$E[\\varepsilon_{it}|\\text{treat}_i, \\text{post}_t, \\alpha_i, \\lambda_t] = 0$\n",
    "\n",
    "**标准误处理**：Bertrand et al.(2004) 指出 DiD 的 SE 应在个体层面聚类，修正序列相关。"
   ]
  },
  {
